"title": "8117: discipleship, benefits of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8117: discipleship, benefits of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Joy, peace and happiness result from following Jesus Christ, together with the hope of being like him and with him in heaven. This is anticipated in the OT, which stresses the importance of obedience to the LORD.</p>\n<h2>Blessings result from obedient discipleship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:28\">LUK 11:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:32\">PRO 8:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:25\">MAT 7:24–7:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:47-Luke6:48\">LUK 6:47–6:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:17\">JHN 13:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:21\">JHN 14:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:25\">JAS 1:25</a></p>\n<h2>Joy results from discipleship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:10-John15:11\">JHN 15:10–15:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:14\">PSA 119:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:52\">ACT 13:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:34\">ACT 16:34</a> <em>the Philippian jailer</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:17\">ROM 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22\">GAL 5:22</a> <em>the fruit of the Spirit</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:25\">PHP 1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:6\">1TH 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:34\">HEB 10:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:6\">1PE 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:8\">1PE 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">JUD 1:24</a></p>\n<h2>Peace results from discipleship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:27\">JHN 14:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:26\">NUM 6:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:8\">PSA 4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:11\">PSA 29:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:11\">PSA 37:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:3\">ISA 26:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28-Matt11:29\">MAT 11:28–11:29</a> <em>Jesus Christ promises rest for the weary</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:14\">LUK 2:14</a> <em>the angels' greeting to the shepherds at the birth of Jesus Christ</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:36\">LUK 24:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:19\">JHN 20:19</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:33\">JHN 16:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:21\">JHN 20:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:26\">JHN 20:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:10\">ROM 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1\">ROM 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:7\">PHP 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:15\">COL 3:15</a></p>\n<h2>True happiness results from discipleship</h2>\n<h3>Happiness flows from doing God's will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:1\">PSA 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:1-Ps119:2\">PSA 119:1–119:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:12\">PSA 94:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:1\">PSA 112:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps128:1\">PSA 128:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:18\">PRO 29:18</a></p>\n<h3>Disciples are truly happy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:3-Matt5:12\">MAT 5:3–5:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:20-Luke6:23\">LUK 6:20–6:23</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:3\">REV 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:14\">REV 22:14</a></p>\n<h2>Disciples are abundantly recompensed in this life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:29-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:29–10:30</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:29-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:29–18:30</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:16\">PRO 15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:8\">PRO 16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:7-Matt7:11\">MAT 7:7–7:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:9-Luke11:13\">LUK 11:9–11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:12\">JHN 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:27\">JHN 10:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:26\">JHN 12:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:31-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:31–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:6\">1TI 6:6</a></p>\n<h2>Disciples are blessed by being united with Jesus Christ in the family of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:46-Matt12:50\">MAT 12:46–12:50</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:31-Mark3:35\">MRK 3:31–3:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:19-Luke8:21\">LUK 8:19–8:21</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:10\">GAL 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:19\">EPH 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:15\">EPH 3:15</a></p>\n<h2>Disciples will be blessed with eternal life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:30\">MRK 10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:30\">LUK 18:30</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:46\">MAT 25:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:7\">ROM 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:8\">GAL 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:2\">1JN 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:11\">1JN 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:13\">1JN 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:20\">1JN 5:20</a></p>\n<h2>Disciples have the hope of being like Jesus Christ and being with him in heaven</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2\">1JN 3:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:26\">JHN 12:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:3\">JHN 14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">ROM 8:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:49\">1CO 15:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:4\">2PE 1:4</a></p>",
